data.description: Welcome Home to this 4 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom colonial home in the Pelham Manor Community. This move-in ready 2020 home has been nicely kept and updated with a hardscaped stone patio, finished garage with showroom epoxy floor & a well landscaped/totally regraded yard. The main floor has a kitchen, living room, dining room, half bath and family room/office space. The second floor has the primary ensuite with walk-in closet, 3 additional bedrooms, an additional bathroom and a laundry space. The fully finished basement has 2 spacious rooms, a potential office/spare room and a full bathroom. Schedule your tour today!!
